column5: Here is a link to a Eagles nest camera with 3 baby eagles. They were born several days apart and range drastically in size. I could watch them all day.  http://www.hancockwildlifechannel.org/stat...090302200021473
Very cool!  Thanks for the link.
Great link! Bookmarked that website for many other things as well. Pretty relaxing bird chirping sounds are driving my cat crazy.
Hear a few cars and airplanes go by.
